data.description: Absolutely stunning open concept home. Kitchen recently updated with granite counters and luxurious tile flooring throughout the downstairs. This amazing layout features a first floor primary bedroom complete with walk in closet and en-suite with jetted soaking tub. Second larger primary bedroom complete with ensuite located upstairs beautifully updated with gorgeous custom tile shower. Enjoy a backyard oasis with large newer full deck which opens up to a relaxing paver patio and fire pit.
